### Correct architectural direction
Validation should be coverage-matrix driven: screen families, dirty names, localization, nested layout, semantic ambiguity, asset stress, keyboard/scroll states, and regression quotas.

### Recommended fix shape
Keep baselines only with explicit budgets and deadlines; fail touched subsystems unless debt decreases. Make advisory failures visible in release summaries and add blocking diversity quotas, not just minimum screen count.

